From 2445b17eae1d5356936a0a598940dfaad469c29d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Shahidan, Muhammad Shahmil" <muhammad.shahmil.shahidan@intel.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Apr 2026 10:25:31 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 02/52] Add serdes drivers

Adding ISX031 driver and max9x serdes drivers into
6.18 kernel from ipu6-drivers repository.

Signed-off-by: Shahidan, Muhammad Shahmil <muhammad.shahmil.shahidan@intel.com>
---
 drivers/media/i2c/isx031.c             | 1133 ++++++++++
 drivers/media/i2c/max9x/Makefile       |   12 +
 drivers/media/i2c/max9x/max9295.c      |  807 +++++++
 drivers/media/i2c/max9x/max9295.h      |  144 ++
 drivers/media/i2c/max9x/max9296.c      |  890 ++++++++
 drivers/media/i2c/max9x/max9296.h      |  145 ++
 drivers/media/i2c/max9x/max96717.c     |  617 ++++++
 drivers/media/i2c/max9x/max96717.h     |   91 +
 drivers/media/i2c/max9x/max96724.c     |  989 +++++++++
 drivers/media/i2c/max9x/max96724.h     |  242 +++
 drivers/media/i2c/max9x/max9x_pdata.h  |  105 +
 drivers/media/i2c/max9x/regmap-retry.c |   52 +
 drivers/media/i2c/max9x/regmap-retry.h |   18 +
 drivers/media/i2c/max9x/serdes.c       | 2721 ++++++++++++++++++++++++
 drivers/media/i2c/max9x/serdes.h       |  459 ++++
 15 files changed, 8425 insertions(+)
